About Us

Fafa's Omega Brick Pavers is a family-owned and operated business that has been providing quality paver services to the Lakeland, FL area for many years. We specialize in both residential and commercial paver installation, repairs, and maintenance. We offer a wide variety of pavers to choose from, so you can find the perfect one for your project.

What we are best at Our Services

  • Paver Installation
    Paver Installation

    Our paver installation service can transform your outdoor living space with beautiful, durable pavers. We'll work with you to design and install a perfect paver patio, driveway, or walkway that fits your needs and budget.

  • Paver Repair
    Paver Repair

    If your pavers are looking a bit worse for wear, our paver repair and sealing service can help. We'll patch up any cracks or holes, then seal the surface to protect it from weathering and staining.

  • Driveways
    Driveways

    Our Driveways service offers homeowners a beautiful and durable solution for their driveway needs. Our pavers are installed by experienced professionals, and we offer a wide variety of colors, styles, and sizes to choose from. We also offer maintenance services to keep your driveway looking its best for years to come.

  • Paver Walkways
    Paver Walkways

    Walkways is a service that allows homeowners to design and customize their own walkway using pavers. This service is unique because it allows homeowners to be creative and choose the colors, shapes, and sizes of their walkway.

  • Paver Steps
    Paver Steps

    If you are looking for a paver company that offers a Steps service, then you have come to the right place. Our Steps service can help make your home look its best by adding beautiful, functional steps to your property.

  • Pool Remodels
    Pool Remodels

    Our Pool Remodels service offers a wide variety of remodeling options for your swimming pool, patio, and backyard area. Our experienced professionals can help you choose the perfect design and materials to create the perfect outdoor space for your home.
